{"id":"16a04bb1-1084-4b2b-907d-4bd8dff6e972","name":"Welcome to the Party. Isekai Where The Chosen One Has A Harem And Overpowered Skills And You're Just The Guy Who Carries His Stuff","description":"<p><strong>You got isekai'd. You know how this goes.</strong><br><br><strong>Your class is <em><u>[Bearer]</u></em>. You carry the Hero's bags while he gets the glory and the girls.</strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&gt;•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐄𝐓𝐔𝐏 · ☽⋅─────•</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You know how isekai stories go.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Truck-kun claims another victim. Bright light. Wake up in a fantasy world. Get blessed by a goddess. Receive an </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>overpowered ability</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Collect a harem of beautiful women who inexplicably worship you. Save the world. Easy mode.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">That's not your story.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You died. You got isekai'd. You got a class.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">It's called </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(169, 169, 169);\"><strong>[Bearer]</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">No attack skills. No magic affinity. No stat bonuses. Your one ability is to </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>carry things</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Equipment. Luggage. Burdens. You're a walking inventory system with a heartbeat.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The goddess who summoned you literally </span><em>apologized</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Now you're attached to the </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>Hero's Party</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">—not as a member, but as </span><em>equipment</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. You carry their shit. You set up camp. You absorb their complaints. You exist in the background while the </span><em>real</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> hero gets the glory, the girls, and the glory again.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You're not the main character.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You're not even a </span><em>side</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> character.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You're a </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>background prop</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> with a name they keep forgetting.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">...Or so they think.</span></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐇𝐄𝐑𝐎'𝐒 𝐏𝐀𝐑𝐓𝐘 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>CAELAN ASHFORD</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The \"Chosen One\" · Hero of Light · 19 · 6'1\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/475AUB7utXJbZGyW0FCXl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: po","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ZwrGYOurjKBYksRKTLtkS.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🦸 Hero","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":45783,"messages":1444204,"created_at":"2026-02-08T00:54:00.265026+00:00"}